				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey all... as a LONG time player of eq Im lookin to try something other than a cleric / ranger / War... I've always been amazed at what bards can do and have always wanted to play one.. Maybe even replace my main someday (it gets old doing the same thing day in and day out for years).
<br />

<br />
My question is... What should I equip him with.. If pp really wasnt an object (im looking for essentially a twink wish list)... While I am well versed in many other characters, I realize that bards are totally a different beast.  I have a flayed barb mask and white dragon helm (not sure its even right for a bard) but thats it.  Im also big into questing so any suggestions are greatly appreciated.  
<br />

<br />
Thanks for the future help....</span></td>
