				<td colspan="2"><span>In my short time as a bard, I've noticed that it isn't so much that putting it in the primary hand is godly, it is more because when you have a secondary only instrument, you need to un equip the primary then the secondary, in order to equip a secondary instrument.
<br />

<br />
Thus, if it was able to be put in the primary slot, you would only have to swap out 1 item, instead of 2.
<br />

<br />
I guess it comes down to a time thing.</span></td>
