				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Lookin to Twink a bard!<a name="39703"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 12 04 10:25 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>just my 2cp with this
<br />

<br />
twinking is not evil as people have made it out, but when combined with powerlevelling it can be very detrimental.
<br />

<br />
my bard is my 3rd toon
<br />

<br />
65 warrior retired
<br />
65 mage retired
<br />
36 bard active
<br />

<br />
when i created him, i gave him the TDoK, primary flute, secondary stringed and trouby mace instrument wise, bought him a small set of acrylia  solstice earring and filled in the rest with stuff off my trader. 
<br />

<br />
When i hit about lvl 30, the guild my mains were in fell apart and i retired my mains (no time to get the requirements for the Big guilds on Xev) and switched out all the good gear that was usuable by the bard that i had on the mage and warrior, hence my lvl 36 bard is called a huge twink. <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
The way i look at it is this, i gave my bard what he needed to get thru the tedious first 15 levels, grouped thru paludal, soloed since in IC/EW (ldon is pretty limited on Xev before level 40) so i do know pulling/solo/group techniques.
<br />

<br />
the gear he has now will serve him right thru to 60ish with some upgrades from LDON and camping along the way. i can concentrate on learning about the class and songs and best ways to implement things based on current senario's without being caught up in the dont have enuff plat for songs/gear crap that most classes experience at one time or another. 
<br />

<br />
But having said all this, as with any other alt i  give the basics too, i learn the class on my own and shy away from powerlevelling, i have had offers from high end friends to have my bard at 65 within a week, but dont want to do this due to the fact that i wont have learnt any of the skills i will need in the future with him along the way.
<br />

<br />
as i said my 2 cp
<br />

<br />
is personal choice, but twink or powerlevel, wouldnt do both
<br />

<br />
Macenion Darksinger
<br />
36th level bard of Xev
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
